.infinite-background.grey ng-controller="ResultsFilterController"
  .panel.filters
    h3.margin-bottom-1
      | Showing all results for "{{$ctrl.filters.name}}"
    .row.collapse
      .columns.small-12.medium-6
        input type="text" ng-model="filters.name"
      .columns.small-12.medium-6.padding-left-2
        button.bg-green-yellow.rounded type="button" ng-click="$ctrl.postSearch()"
          | Search
    .row.collapse.margin-bottom-1
      .columns.small-12
        span
          ' Looking for a more specific search?
        a ui-sref="search({searchType: 'criteria'})"
          | Try searching with search criteria.

